1
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:46,280
Miss Xie

2
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,560
It seems very soon

3
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:50,599
I'll have to start calling you my sister-in-law

4
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:55,519
You two go ahead and talk

5
00:01:55,519 --> 00:01:56,760
I'll go get some hot water

6
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,120
Director Hirata

7
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:21,199
Miss Xie is so gentle and charming

8
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:23,800
She and Mr. Liang are a perfect match

9
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,039
I was a bit reckless just now

10
00:02:26,599 --> 00:02:28,319
I hope Mr. Liang won't mind

11
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,240
Not at all

12
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:34,199
It's all for the new government and the Empire

13
00:02:34,879 --> 00:02:35,960
Director Hirata

14
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,319
You act with fairness and authority

15
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,800
And never show favoritism

16
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:40,520
Truly admirable

17
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,400
I'm relieved that Mr. Liang is all right

18
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:46,120
But I still want to remind you

19
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:47,960
Be extra careful these days

20
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,960
Rest well in the hospital

21
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:52,360
Thank you for your concern, Director Hirata

22
00:02:53,719 --> 00:02:55,360
The peace conference is about to begin

23
00:02:55,680 --> 00:02:57,120
I was assigned this task at the last minute

24
00:02:57,400 --> 00:02:59,159
There are many urgent matters to resolve

25
00:02:59,599 --> 00:03:00,639
Lying here

26
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,800
I'm afraid I can't really relax

27
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:05,159
Work is important

28
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:07,319
But your health matters even more

29
00:03:08,280 --> 00:03:09,080
Director Cui

30
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,439
Let's let him rest

31
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,280
Brother Liang

32
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:14,639
We'll be going now

33
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,319
Take good care of your injuries

34
00:03:16,599 --> 00:03:17,719
I'll come visit you in a few days

35
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,639
The statements of the two are basically the same.

36
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,199
But no matter how you look at it, Chief Hirata,

37
00:03:58,360 --> 00:03:59,800
it seems you still have doubts.

38
00:04:00,599 --> 00:04:01,560
What do you think?

39
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,039
The injuries on his body—

40
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,439
if it were an ordinary person,

41
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,599
they would have died several times over.

42
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:10,599
The anti-Japanese elements really wanted him dead.

43
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,680
So there’s definitely no problem with Liang Shuo.

44
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:15,000
As for Miss Xie,

45
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,279
that’s still up for discussion.

46
00:04:18,519 --> 00:04:19,240
Chief Hirata,

47
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,560
I still have matters to attend to at my office.

48
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:21,600
I’ll take my leave for now.

49
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,600
Miss Hirata

50
00:04:29,319 --> 00:04:30,199
Director Lu

51
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:31,920
What brings you here?

52
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:34,879
Director Liang was just appointed and already faced an assassination attempt.

53
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:37,079
It certainly caused a sensation throughout the city.

54
00:04:37,279 --> 00:04:38,199
With something this significant,

55
00:04:38,319 --> 00:04:39,600
as the Director of Supervision,

56
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,279
I naturally can't stay uninvolved.

57
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:42,800
Of course.

58
00:04:43,439 --> 00:04:44,279
Given your

59
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,920
ability to gather intelligence,

60
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:46,519
I assume

61
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,000
you already have some understanding

62
00:04:48,199 --> 00:04:49,160
of what happened.

63
00:04:50,439 --> 00:04:52,079
The girl by Liang Shuo's side

64
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:54,240
showed up a little too coincidentally.

65
00:04:54,759 --> 00:04:55,959
What do you think, Director Lu?

66
00:04:56,199 --> 00:04:57,959
I'm not entirely clear on this matter yet.

67
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:01,439
But I trust you have your own judgment, Miss Hirata.

68
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,839
Are you alright?

69
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,439
I'm fine.

70
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,480
Hirata asked me a few questions.

71
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:11,000
I used an alias.

72
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:13,079
I don't think I gave anything away.

73
00:05:13,519 --> 00:05:15,839
Luckily, we exchanged information in advance.

74
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:20,040
She won't drop her suspicions so quickly.

75
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,360
We still need to make plans early.

76
00:05:23,759 --> 00:05:24,879
She asked for my address.

77
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:27,000
She'll definitely send someone to search.

78
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:29,439
Is there anything suspicious at home?

79
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,680
Don't worry.

80
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:32,720
I won't bring those things home.

81
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:33,800
Besides,

82
00:05:34,000 --> 00:05:35,600
I'm using a public identity.

83
00:05:38,399 --> 00:05:39,240
Chief

84
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,279
This is Liang Shuo's attending physician.

85
00:05:43,439 --> 00:05:44,360
Dr. Xu

86
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,800
Thank you for your hard work, Dr. Xu.

87
00:05:47,279 --> 00:05:49,079
This is Director Lu from the Special Agent Headquarters' Inspection Department.

88
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:50,839
Mr. Liang

89
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:52,920
How is his current condition?

90
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,000
He's fine for now.

91
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,759
Please don't worry, Chief.

92
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,040
I was just about to do my rounds.

93
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:58,759
Understood.

94
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,399
Just in case.

95
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,319
You still need to go back.

96
00:06:05,399 --> 00:06:06,199
What about you?

97
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,879
I'm going back to No. 76.

98
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:11,079
I'll find a way to keep an eye on Hirata Xizi.

99
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,399
Hopefully, she'll be cleared of suspicion soon.

100
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:17,000
What about your injury?

101
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:18,079
It's not fatal.

102
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:19,839
The bleeding has stopped.

103
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:20,959
Don't worry.

104
00:06:21,240 --> 00:06:22,519
I can't help but worry.

105
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:24,319
You can't just tough it out like this.

106
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:29,439
You wouldn't listen to me anyway.

107
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,920
Director Liang is fine now.

108
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:34,360
I'd like you to help me investigate this young woman.

109
00:06:34,480 --> 00:06:35,680
Xie Yuxin

110
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:38,399
Her address is 16 Chunhua Road.

111
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,959
Lead a team there yourself.

112
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:44,120
Don't miss a single clue.

113
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,319
Alright.

114
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:50,040
I'm also curious to find out.

115
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,680
Just who is this Miss Xie, really?

116
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:55,079
Then I'll leave it to Miss Hirata.

117
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,680
Please send my regards to Director Liang.

118
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,279
Wish him a speedy recovery.

119
00:06:58,480 --> 00:06:59,279
No problem.

120
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,160
Where did this ring come from?

121
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,519
Ever since Cui Mo first saw you,

122
00:07:22,519 --> 00:07:23,959
I was already prepared.

123
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,199
Always leave yourself a way out.

124
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,759
Especially in our line of work.

125
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:36,319
What's wrong?

126
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,319
Nothing.

127
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:40,000
Mr. Liang,

128
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,800
since you're so generous

129
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:44,920
and willingly gave me this ring,

130
00:07:45,079 --> 00:07:46,360
now that it's in my pocket,

131
00:07:46,600 --> 00:07:48,319
don't think about getting it back.

132
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,199
Are you like a Pixiu or something?

133
00:07:59,079 --> 00:07:59,839
Come in.

134
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,000
So, what should we do next...

135
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:18,240
Don't put it there.

136
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:26,519
Put it on the cart.

137
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,759
You're Chinese?

138
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,559
I'm your attending physician.

139
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:34,679
Xu Wen.

140
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,440
A Chinese.

141
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,399
Working at a Japanese Army hospital.

142
00:08:39,399 --> 00:08:40,559
That's quite rare.

143
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:42,879
I studied abroad in Japan,

144
00:08:42,879 --> 00:08:45,399
at Sendai Medical College as a Chinese student.

145
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,960
Just like you, Mr. Liang,

146
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:49,320
I admire Chairman Wang's peace movement.

147
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:51,159
After graduation, I came to work here.

148
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,960
Director Hirata instructed me

149
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,159
to pay close attention to your health.

150
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:57,399
Thank you for your concern.

151
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,759
Actually, my injury isn't serious.

152
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,759
It's my job.

153
00:09:13,679 --> 00:09:14,399
Mr. Liang,

154
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:15,639
now I need to check your wound.

155
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:16,759
Let me examine it.

156
00:09:20,759 --> 00:09:21,240
Alright.

157
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,200
Look straight ahead.

158
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:44,120
Mr. Liang's condition is not serious.

159
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,000
At the moment,

160
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,799
it's just caused by the impact.

161
00:09:46,799 --> 00:09:48,039
He experienced temporary shock.

162
00:09:48,039 --> 00:09:49,200
He'll be fine after resting for a couple of days.

163
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,879
The bandage on his head needs to be changed regularly.

164
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:55,120
A nurse will come to check on him at regular intervals.

165
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:56,960
That's not necessary.

166
00:09:57,240 --> 00:09:59,399
I'll go handle the discharge procedures right away.

167
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,279
If Mr. Liang wants to leave,

168
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,519
I have no right to stop him.

169
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,720
But for the sake of your health,

170
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,639
I still hope you'll come back for a follow-up.

171
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,200
If it's really inconvenient,

172
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:10,480
we can also visit you at home.

173
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:16,000
Sorry to trouble you, then.

174
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:36,240
Traitor.

175
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,559
So shameless.

176
00:10:39,279 --> 00:10:40,600
Wang Jingwei's remarks

177
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,720
have indeed influenced many Chinese students in Japan.

178
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,360
When he came in just now, he didn't say a word.

179
00:10:46,559 --> 00:10:47,480
You exposed him,

180
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:49,200
and only then did he admit he was Chinese.

181
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:50,840
He's very cunning.

182
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:55,759
We'll just have to be more vigilant ourselves.

183
00:11:21,480 --> 00:11:21,960
Director.

184
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,759
I've checked everything.

185
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,080
It's all clean.

186
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,480
I don't see any problems.

187
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:41,440
Stand up.

188
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,000
Again.

189
00:11:46,399 --> 00:11:47,159
Again.

190
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:51,600
Again.

191
00:11:51,919 --> 00:11:52,799
Stand up.

192
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:56,159
Again.

193
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,039
Senior, how are you?

194
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:19,919
I'm fine.

195
00:12:21,000 --> 00:12:22,440
But I see you're hurt.

196
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:30,240
Does it still hurt?

197
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,080
It's fine.

198
00:12:32,559 --> 00:12:33,159
It doesn't hurt.

199
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,279
It's okay.

200
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,200
It's already been investigated.

201
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,039
This Miss Xie previously

202
00:12:50,039 --> 00:12:53,000
did indeed study at Nanyang Girls' School.

203
00:12:53,159 --> 00:12:55,080
She is also currently working at a clothing store.

204
00:12:55,080 --> 00:12:56,759
Her background checks out.

205
00:12:58,360 --> 00:13:00,240
Did you check the jewelry store?

206
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,159
I've already asked the owner about that.

207
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:04,279
Director Liang went there on the 23rd of last month

208
00:13:04,279 --> 00:13:05,799
to order a ring.

209
00:13:05,799 --> 00:13:07,399
The style he wanted

210
00:13:07,399 --> 00:13:09,039
wasn't in stock at the store.

211
00:13:09,039 --> 00:13:11,240
Director Liang was very generous.

212
00:13:11,240 --> 00:13:13,320
He paid a large sum of money.

213
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:14,840
The item was ordered from Hong Kong, China.

214
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:15,840
Understood.

215
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:18,279
How are things on Lu Xijian's side?

216
00:13:18,519 --> 00:13:20,519
Miss Xie's residence has been searched.

217
00:13:20,919 --> 00:13:23,360
Director Lu reported that nothing unusual was found.

218
00:13:23,919 --> 00:13:25,159
What about progressive books?

219
00:13:26,600 --> 00:13:27,559
None were found.

220
00:13:28,039 --> 00:13:29,000
For a student,

221
00:13:29,240 --> 00:13:31,759
it's unusually clean.

222
00:13:32,399 --> 00:13:33,000
Got it.

223
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:41,919
Teacher

224
00:13:42,639 --> 00:13:43,759
We've found their whereabouts.

225
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:45,159
According to the informant,

226
00:13:45,159 --> 00:13:47,200
Liang Shuo and Miss were chased by assassins.

227
00:13:47,240 --> 00:13:48,399
They are now out of danger.

228
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,519
Liang Shuo is slightly injured.

229
00:13:49,639 --> 00:13:51,279
He is recovering at the Japanese Army Hospital.

230
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:53,840
But Miss

231
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,200
has been unreachable.

232
00:13:56,879 --> 00:13:57,879
We can't reach her.

233
00:13:59,039 --> 00:14:00,000
Keep waiting.

234
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:04,879
Teacher

235
00:14:05,399 --> 00:14:06,039
This is

236
00:14:06,879 --> 00:14:08,480
a telegram from Chongqing.

237
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:12,720
Old Liu has realized the seriousness of the situation.

238
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:14,600
He confronted Mr. Dai.

239
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:16,399
He wanted to come to Shanghai to assist us.

240
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:17,720
But he was refused.

241
00:14:18,639 --> 00:14:19,559
It's really hard to believe

242
00:14:20,519 --> 00:14:22,200
that this old fox

243
00:14:22,679 --> 00:14:23,919
would do such a thing.

244
00:14:25,519 --> 00:14:26,639
The situation is so unfavorable.

245
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:28,519
If we wait for Miss to meet the informant,

246
00:14:28,519 --> 00:14:29,679
I'm afraid it will delay things.

247
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:31,200
I'll make a trip to the hospital.

248
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:32,120
To gather some information.

249
00:14:32,120 --> 00:14:32,799
No.

250
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:34,360
At this time,

251
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,320
we absolutely can't act rashly.

252
00:14:38,120 --> 00:14:38,679
Yes.

253
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:50,559
Tomorrow, have the informant

254
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:52,440
wait near Miss's safe house.

255
00:14:52,519 --> 00:14:53,480
Bring the token.

256
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,960
If Miss sees it,

257
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,039
she will naturally come to meet.

258
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,159
Be careful not to expose yourself.

259
00:14:59,320 --> 00:14:59,879
Yes.

260
00:15:08,360 --> 00:15:09,399
We still need to be cautious.

261
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:10,519
We can't let our guard down.

262
00:15:10,519 --> 00:15:11,519
Keep a close watch.

263
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,919
I'll make you something delicious later.

264
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,120
Buy a pack of cigarettes.

265
00:15:57,279 --> 00:15:57,919
Get lost.

266
00:16:19,519 --> 00:16:20,039
Hello.

267
00:16:20,039 --> 00:16:20,840
Are you looking to buy a painting?

268
00:16:21,759 --> 00:16:22,679
Take a look inside.

269
00:16:24,559 --> 00:16:27,200
These are all masterpieces by French masters.

270
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:28,399
They're called oil paintings.

271
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:29,279
Take a look.

272
00:16:29,360 --> 00:16:30,279
Look at these colors.

273
00:16:30,879 --> 00:16:31,840
And the brushwork.

274
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,200
And this painting as well.

275
00:16:34,519 --> 00:16:37,240
I think this one is the best.

276
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,240
This one is also nice.

277
00:16:47,279 --> 00:16:48,879
Madam, you have excellent taste.

278
00:16:49,159 --> 00:16:50,840
This is a newly arrived painting.

279
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,720
Have a look.

280
00:16:52,399 --> 00:16:53,360
I'll take this one.

281
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,000
Alright.

282
00:17:10,839 --> 00:17:13,039
There are spies at 16 Chunhua Road.

283
00:17:13,599 --> 00:17:15,039
There's something suspicious about Xie Yuxin.

284
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,240
I see.

285
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,440
Go pay Miss Xie a visit.

286
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,440
