00:37:19,159 --> 00:37:21,360
It's over, something big has happened

578
00:38:15,840 --> 00:38:16,599
What is she doing?

579
00:38:16,599 --> 00:38:17,360
Go inside and talk.

580
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,320
Hirata tortured her.

581
00:39:00,920 --> 00:39:02,119
Her bones were injured.

582
00:39:03,639 --> 00:39:04,559
I'll think of something right away.

583
00:39:04,559 --> 00:39:05,599
I'll get someone to fetch medicine.

584
00:39:08,719 --> 00:39:09,960
We owe it to you this time.

585
00:39:12,840 --> 00:39:14,239
It was Old Tan who made the quick decision.

586
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,559
I was just following orders.

587
00:39:16,159 --> 00:39:17,599
As for Miss Xie,

588
00:39:18,199 --> 00:39:19,480
everything has been taken care of.

589
00:39:21,079 --> 00:39:22,320
She still can't go back.

590
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:25,360
The military police are definitely investigating along the river.

591
00:39:25,679 --> 00:39:27,400
We'd better be careful.

592
00:39:27,800 --> 00:39:29,079
You can't stay long either.

593
00:39:29,719 --> 00:39:31,159
Hirata Xizi is dead.

594
00:39:32,199 --> 00:39:33,639
The intelligence headquarters

595
00:39:33,639 --> 00:39:35,320
will probably summon you soon.

596
00:39:37,840 --> 00:39:38,800
Then, as for her,

597
00:39:39,440 --> 00:39:40,559
I'll leave her in your care.

598
00:39:45,320 --> 00:39:46,400
Our goal

599
00:39:46,639 --> 00:39:48,280
is to save our compatriots, isn't it?

600
00:39:51,119 --> 00:39:51,760
Yes.

601
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:54,119
I was being foolish.

602
00:39:57,480 --> 00:39:58,559
She probably already knows

603
00:39:58,559 --> 00:40:00,119
our true identities.

604
00:40:00,880 --> 00:40:01,880
I think

605
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:02,880
we should still report

606
00:40:02,880 --> 00:40:04,239
this situation to the organization.

607
00:40:05,960 --> 00:40:07,280
I'll tell Old Tan.

608
00:40:10,519 --> 00:40:11,440
I'll go now.

609
00:40:14,599 --> 00:40:15,400
Liang Shuo,

610
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:22,480
I'm glad

611
00:40:23,039 --> 00:40:24,559
that when you needed help,

612
00:40:25,599 --> 00:40:27,079
you thought of me first.
